name: mountain mover
description:
technomancers were said to have regularly congregated on mountaintops, journeying great distances to temporarily escape the clutches of urban dystopia. after analyzing the sediment of these excavation areas, archeologists have concluded that practitioners must have utilized a form of audio-vibrational wizardry to reshape the structure of these colossal landmarks.

cast to invoke amplitude. inscribed by tenorless circa 2022 // elements collection [fire]

one of three artifacts from technomancy beta test 0.1
